name: Orbital Error
description: Hover cursor/slide ← → ↑↓  to interact. -> As the ship approached the exit from hyperspace, Lucy took out a weird looking small contraption from her bag and slowly placed under her tounge. As the ship exited from hyperspace Lucy felt the ship shake and heard the voice of John, who had a tone of seriousness, say "The ship is experiencing technical difficulties. The ship is going to enter an orbit around the 4th moon of the planet."
